---
layout: layouts/page.njk
title: Floor Plans
metaTitle: "Senior Living Floor Plans — Studios to 2-Bedroom Suites | Azalea Estates"
description: "Four senior apartment floor plans at Azalea Estates in Fayetteville, GA. Studios, one-bedroom, and two-bedroom deluxe suites — all with private baths, kitchenettes, and garden views."
eyebrow: Find Your Fit
pageIntro: "Four spacious floor plans from efficient studios to roomy two-bedroom deluxe suites. Every one with a private bath, kitchen or kitchenette, personal thermostat, and a window with a view."
eleventyComputed:
  pageHero: "{{ images.livingRoom }}"
permalink: /floor-plans/
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-heading reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Featured Floor Plans</span>
      <h2>Choose the space that fits your story.</h2>
      <p>Every apartment at Azalea Estates offers a private bath, ample closet space, an individually controllable thermostat, and windows overlooking our landscaped grounds.</p>
    </div>

    {#
      Each "Request pricing" is a <button> that opens the modal below and
      carries the plan details via data-* attributes. The JS reads these and
      populates hidden form fields, plus updates the visible modal heading.
    #}
    {%- set plans = [
      { tag: 'Studio',              name: 'The Magnolia',  size: '385',  bed: 1, bath: 1,
        features: ['Efficient open layout', 'Full private bath', 'Kitchenette', 'Landscape view window'] },
      { tag: 'One Bedroom',         name: 'The Dogwood',   size: '408',  bed: 1, bath: 1,
        features: ['Separate bedroom', 'Living area with seating', 'Kitchenette', 'Ample closet storage'] },
      { tag: 'One Bedroom Deluxe',  name: 'The Camellia',  size: '624',  bed: 1, bath: 1,
        features: ['Expanded living and dining areas', 'Generous bedroom suite', 'Full kitchenette', 'Walk-in closet'] },
      { tag: 'Two Bedroom',         name: 'The Hydrangea', size: '680',  bed: 2, bath: 1,
        features: ['Two private bedrooms', 'Shared living &amp; dining', 'Kitchenette', 'Ideal for couples'] },
      { tag: 'Two Bedroom Deluxe',  name: 'The Azalea',    size: '925',  bed: 2, bath: 2,
        features: ['Two bedrooms, two baths', 'Expansive living and dining', 'Full kitchen', 'Premium finishes'] }
    ] -%}

    <div class="plans-grid">
      {% for p in plans %}
      <div class="plan-card reveal">
        <span class="plan-card__tag">{{ p.tag }}</span>
        <h3>{{ p.name }}</h3>
        <div class="plan-card__specs">
          <span><strong>{{ p.size }}</strong> sq. ft.</span>
          <span><strong>{{ p.bed }}</strong> Bed</span>
          <span><strong>{{ p.bath }}</strong> Bath</span>
        </div>
        <ul>
          {% for f in p.features %}<li>{{ f | safe }}</li>{% endfor %}
        </ul>
        <button type="button"
                class="btn btn--ghost plan-card__cta"
                data-open-plan-modal
                data-plan-name="{{ p.name }}"
                data-plan-type="{{ p.tag }}"
                data-plan-specs="{{ p.size }} sq. ft., {{ p.bed }} bed, {{ p.bath }} bath"
                aria-haspopup="dialog"
                aria-controls="planModal">
          Request pricing
        </button>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}

      <div class="plan-card reveal" style="background: var(--c-ink); color: var(--c-cream); border-color: var(--c-ink);">
        <span class="plan-card__tag" style="color: var(--c-accent-soft);">Personalized</span>
        <h3 style="color: var(--c-cream);">Not sure yet?</h3>
        <p style="color: rgba(250, 246, 241, 0.85);">We&rsquo;ll walk you through availability, current pricing, and help you find the right fit based on your needs and preferences.</p>
        <button type="button"
                class="btn btn--primary"
                style="margin-top: var(--space-3);"
                data-open-plan-modal
                data-plan-name="No specific plan yet"
                data-plan-type="Help me choose"
                data-plan-specs="Open to recommendations"
                aria-haspopup="dialog"
                aria-controls="planModal">
          Talk to Admissions
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{#
  Plan Inquiry Modal
  Accessibility:
    role="dialog" + aria-modal="true" creates a modal context.
    aria-labelledby points at the visible heading.
    Starts hidden from AT via hidden + aria-hidden; JS toggles state.
    On open, focus moves into the dialog; on close, returns to the trigger.
    Escape and backdrop-click close the dialog (WCAG 2.1.2 + 2.4.3).
#}
<div class="modal" id="planModal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="planModalHeading" hidden>
  <div class="modal__backdrop" data-modal-close aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="modal__panel">
    <button type="button" class="modal__close" aria-label="Close dialog" data-modal-close>
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"/><line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"/></svg>
    </button>

    <div class="modal__header">
      <span class="eyebrow">Floor Plan Inquiry</span>
      <h2 id="planModalHeading">
        Request info about <span data-plan-display-name>our floor plans</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="modal__sub">
        <span data-plan-display-type>Any layout</span>
        <span data-plan-display-divider aria-hidden="true"> · </span>
        <span data-plan-display-specs></span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <form name="floor-plan-inquiry"
          method="POST"
          action="/contact/thanks/"
          data-netlify="true"
          netlify-honeypot="bot-field"
          class="form modal__form">
      <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="floor-plan-inquiry">
      <input type="hidden" name="plan-name" data-plan-hidden-name value="">
      <input type="hidden" name="plan-type" data-plan-hidden-type value="">
      <input type="hidden" name="plan-specs" data-plan-hidden-specs value="">
      <p class="form-hp" aria-hidden="true">
        <label>Leave this field empty: <input name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off"></label>
      </p>

      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="plan-first-name">First name <span class="form-req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
          <input id="plan-first-name" type="text" name="first_name" autocomplete="given-name" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="plan-last-name">Last name <span class="form-req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
          <input id="plan-last-name" type="text" name="last_name" autocomplete="family-name" required>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="plan-email">Email <span class="form-req" aria-hidden="true">*</span></label>
          <input id="plan-email" type="email" name="email" autocomplete="email" required>
        </div>
        <div class="form-field">
          <label for="plan-phone">Phone</label>
          <input id="plan-phone" type="tel" name="phone" autocomplete="tel">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label for="plan-timeframe">When are you looking to move?</label>
        <select id="plan-timeframe" name="timeframe">
          <option value="">Select a timeframe</option>
          <option value="Within 30 days">Within 30 days</option>
          <option value="1-3 months">1–3 months</option>
          <option value="3-6 months">3–6 months</option>
          <option value="Just exploring">Just exploring for now</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <label for="plan-message">Questions or details</label>
        <textarea id="plan-message" name="message" rows="3" placeholder="Anything specific you'd like to know?"></textarea>
      </div>

      <div class="modal__actions">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn--outline" data-modal-close>Cancel</button>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn--primary">Send Inquiry</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container container--narrow prose reveal">
    <span class="eyebrow">What&rsquo;s Included</span>
    <h2>The monthly rate covers more than you might expect.</h2>
    <p>At Azalea Estates, your monthly rental fee covers all utilities and cable (except telephone), complete building WiFi, weekly housekeeping and linen service, emergency notification systems with personal pendants and bathroom pull cords, three daily chef-prepared meals, and access to every wellness, social, and community amenity on campus.</p>
    <p>Assisted living care is offered in flexible, tiered levels so you only pay for the level of personal support you actually need &mdash; with the ability to adjust as your needs change. Read more about <a href="/living-options/">our independent and assisted living options</a> or browse <a href="/amenities/">what&rsquo;s included at every level</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

